Quickstrike:



Quickstrike jerked his head up, seeing Blackarchnia walk away. He got 
up and trotted to her. He almost stumbled, too much in a hurry. He 
grabbed her around the waist with a grin on his slim face. 

"Howdy sugar-bot," he said. He was still hungry. "Say, ya hungry? Ah 
sure am."
